<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Phylogram of Celoporthe from a Maximum Likelihood analysis, based on combined ITS, BT 1, BT 2 and TEF genes. MP, ML and BI bootstrap support values are shown in order. The tree is rooted with Aurifilum marmelostroma and Holocryphia capensis. Strains in the current study are in blue." , "Figure 2. Morphology of Celoporthe guangdongensis from Sonneratia apetala. A. Conidiomata; B. Transverse sections through conidiomata; C-D. Conidiophores; E-G. Conidia. Scale bars: B = 100 μm; C-G = 10 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/450200" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/417597" .

